OL,3,CRare three-banded armadillo baby takes
OL,4,Cfirst steps outdoor
OL,6,FA rare breed of armadillo has taken
OL,7,Fits first steps into the wild at a zoo
OL,8,Fin Telford.
OL,10,FThe newborn three-banded armadillo at
OL,11,FExotic Zoo was the first recorded
OL,12,Fbirth of the species in a UK zoo in
OL,13,Fover ten years.
OL,15,FIt's found in the wild in Brazil.
OL,16,FZookeepers have been celebrating the
OL,17,Fnewborn's birth due to the armadillo
OL,18,Fstruggling to breed in captivity.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
