OL,3,CRare three-banded armadillo baby takes
OL,4,Cfirst steps outdoor
OL,6,FHowever, the zoo's animal team had to
OL,7,Fstep in due to its mother, Melon,
OL,8,Fdeciding to reject her baby.
OL,10,FDuring the past six weeks, keepers
OL,11,Fhave been feeding the young armadillo
OL,12,Fthroughout the day and night.
OL,14,FNow the zoo says due to this
OL,15,Fprogramme, the baby armadillo is
OL,16,F"thriving" and taking its first steps
OL,17,Foutdoors.
