OL,3,CRare three-banded armadillo baby takes
OL,4,Cfirst steps outdoor
OL,6,FThree-banded armadillos are best known
OL,7,Ffor their ability to roll into a tight
OL,8,Fball when threatened, and are one of
OL,9,Fthe few species armadillo able to do
OL,10,Fso completely.
